Installation instructions:
+------------------------+

Upgrade the packages as root:
# upgradepkg sendmail-8.14.9-i486-1_slack14.1.txz sendmail-cf-8.14.9-noarch-1_slack14.1.txz

Then, restart sendmail:
# sh /etc/rc.d/rc.sendmail restart


